rows.label: tlk43300011_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Ever heard of Cunning Saggie?
You can find it out back in Invidia's
Minnet Terrace.

rows.label: tlk43300011_02_msg0002
rows.name:
That thing was clever enough to have
my old man's arm off in a fight. This
was back in his soldiering days.

rows.label: tlk43300011_02_msg0003
rows.name:
In fact, that's where its name
comes from. They don't call it
cunning for nothing!

rows.label: tlk43300011_02_msg0004
rows.name:
You never know when you'll bump
into tough critters like that. Just
whatever you do, don't get too cocky.

rows.label: tlk43300011_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Not unless you wanna end up in
retirement like my old man.
